commit message: Don't close launcher when sending from clipboard (fixes #5) as this isn't done for the other buttons.
Preserve dialog shown by IntentIntegrator to install Barcode Scanner (fixes #4)
Split Metrics into separate classes for each code type.
Use menu button to advance for now (addresses #8)
Only treat a byte segment as the entire data block if it is at least as long as the content text.  Fixes #6
Set the decoding charset to ISO-8859-1 rather than trying to fudge the conversion by hand.
Change code size with volume keys.
Added instructions for communicating with the terminal.

Match orientation of Receive to Barcode Scanner.

Reduces animation and delay between scans.  Also removed activity label cruft.
Update sample commands to give correct code #

Merge pull request #14 from svetlemodry/master

Czech translation update

zbarcam example: use head -1 instead of dd

This removes the trailing linebreak when the last block is smaller than
the blocksize.
